sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant HA as Home Assistant
  participant API as /agent/run
  participant State as Runtime state builder
  participant Orch as Orchestrator
  participant Factory as ActionFactory
  participant Run as Runner
  participant Registry as ToolBehaviorRegistry
  participant Behavior as ToolBehavior
  participant Tool as HA tool client
  participant HAApi as HA service API
  participant Log as JSONL log

  User->>HA: trigger Night Mode scene / script
  HA->>API: POST /agent/run {intent: night_mode}
  API->>State: build_runtime_state()
  Note over State: merge beliefs + prefs\nno HA pre-read required for night_mode
  State-->>API: runtime state
  API->>Orch: handle_request(night_mode, state)

  alt policy allows action
    Orch->>Factory: build LightAction + SpeechAction
    Factory-->>Orch: typed actions
    Orch-->>API: actions [light.set off, tts.say]
    API->>Run: execute_actions()
    Run->>Registry: for_call(light.set)
    Registry-->>Run: LightSetBehavior
    Run->>Tool: execute(light.set)
    Tool->>HAApi: call services
    HAApi-->>Tool: tool responses
    Tool-->>Run: ToolResult
    Run->>Behavior: verify(light.set, result)
    Run->>Tool: execute(tts.say)
    Run->>Log: tool_result + verification
    API-->>HA: decision + execution
  else policy denies action
    Orch->>Factory: build SpeechAction
    Factory-->>Orch: typed actions
    Orch-->>API: deny + fallback tts.say
    API->>Run: execute_actions()
    Run->>Log: denial result
    API-->>HA: decision + execution
  end

  HA-->>User: spoken confirmation
